node.text:
Omg guys I’ve seriously been dreaming of this moment my whole life! My journey here started with a palette and brushes just playing with makeup in front of a camera not knowing my life would change forever! It has truly been a dream come true thanks to each and everyone of you. As the Leo that I am you already know I had to celebrate my 30th birthday with a bang! I’m so excited to announce @exocosmetics first palette and brushes set! ! This birthday collection will drop 07.31 at 10am PST. ✨
🎥 : @7labrada7

node.text:
I feel so emotional writing this and wondering where did the time go? Although Camila can’t read this I want to just share with you all how blessed I feel to be her mommy. Becoming a mother has been one of the biggest gifts that life has given me, it not only changed the world around me but changed me to be the person I am today. 
...................................................................
A year ago today I was anticipating the moment of meeting you. Wondering who you would be like? Would you look like mommy? Would you look like daddy? Even tho you are the spitting image of your father down to your personality I grew you inside of me and loved you before even meeting you. You’re such a smart, funny and beautiful little girl. Thank you for changing my life and filling me with so much love & happiness. I love you. Happy Birthday. 🤍

Omg guys I’ve seriously been dreaming of this moment my whole life! My journey here started with a palette and brushes just playing with makeup in front of a camera not knowing my life would change forever! It has truly been a dream come true thanks to each and everyone of you. As the Leo that I am you already know I had to celebrate my 30th birthday with a bang! I’m so excited to announce @exocosmetics first palette and brushes set! ! This birthday collection will drop 07.31 at 10am PST. ✨
🎥 : @7labrada7
